{
  "lesson": "WC-09-01",
  "audioMaster": "training/module09-digital/WC-09-01-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 229.956,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Open the Digital module.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 1.636,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "The sidebar splits in two.",
      "startS": 2.186,
      "endS": 3.939,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "The top group, Customer Portal, runs the surfaces your members sign into.",
      "startS": 4.261,
      "endS": 8.524,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "Five entries.",
      "startS": 8.822,
      "endS": 9.722,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "The mobile pages sit below, but those are the next lesson.",
      "startS": 10.139,
      "endS": 13.28,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Click Portal Members.",
      "startS": 13.77,
      "endS": 15.115,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "This is your roster of everyone who holds a portal login.",
      "startS": 15.541,
      "endS": 18.782,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "When a customer says the website won't let them in, this is where you start.",
      "startS": 19.225,
      "endS": 23.311,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Four numbers across the top.",
      "startS": 23.76,
      "endS": 25.367,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "Registered members, how many were active this month, how many joined this week,",
      "startS": 25.988,
      "endS": 27.142,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "and the share who reach you on mobile.",
      "startS": 27.357,
      "endS": 28.91,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "One glance sizes the portal and shows how live it is.",
      "startS": 29.122,
      "endS": 32.288,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "That mobile share matters, since most portal traffic now comes through the app.",
      "startS": 33.031,
      "endS": 40.826,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Below sit three cards.",
      "startS": 41.331,
      "endS": 42.996,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Growth over the year, the plan mix with unlimited monthly the biggest slice,",
      "startS": 43.504,
      "endS": 44.696,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "and account health split into active, inactive, and suspended.",
      "startS": 45.007,
      "endS": 48.075,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Watch that suspended slice;",
      "startS": 48.498,
      "endS": 52.149,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "it's where locked-out members surface before they call.",
      "startS": 52.614,
      "endS": 57.092,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Now the roster itself.",
      "startS": 57.52,
      "endS": 58.765,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "New Record and Export sit top-right, a search box and Filters just under them.",
      "startS": 59.407,
      "endS": 61.924,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Today you're only reading, so leave Export alone.",
      "startS": 62.281,
      "endS": 64.591,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "It sends data out, and this is a look-only tour.",
      "startS": 65.151,
      "endS": 70.834,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Six columns.",
      "startS": 71.28,
      "endS": 72.356,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Name, email, when they joined, their plan, portal status, and last login.",
      "startS": 72.806,
      "endS": 73.29,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Portal status is your first stop when someone can't reach the website:",
      "startS": 73.656,
      "endS": 75.322,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "it tells you whether their access is even active.",
      "startS": 75.604,
      "endS": 76.241,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Last login backs it up, showing when they were really here.",
      "startS": 76.566,
      "endS": 88.23,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Down at the foot: rows per page, a record count, and the pager.",
      "startS": 88.878,
      "endS": 89.561,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Reading, paging, and searching change nothing.",
      "startS": 89.816,
      "endS": 92.948,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "New Record would open a create form,",
      "startS": 93.765,
      "endS": 96.307,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "but that form didn't load during verification, so we leave it parked.",
      "startS": 96.824,
      "endS": 102.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "Back to the sidebar.",
      "startS": 102.72,
      "endS": 103.871,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Click Booking Page.",
      "startS": 104.092,
      "endS": 105.342,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "The admin chrome disappears.",
      "startS": 106.147,
      "endS": 107.774,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "What loads is the customer's own booking site,",
      "startS": 107.988,
      "endS": 114.461,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "with its own branding and a five step wizard that runs from service to confirm.",
      "startS": 115.275,
      "endS": 117.73,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Step one offers three service categories: an inspection, an oil change, and detailing.",
      "startS": 117.948,
      "endS": 120.617,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Read that first screen, then stop.",
      "startS": 121.144,
      "endS": 123.057,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Advancing the wizard books a real visit, so Continue never gets clicked.",
      "startS": 123.37,
      "endS": 127.301,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Portal Messages next.",
      "startS": 127.76,
      "endS": 129.224,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "This is where member messages land and get worked.",
      "startS": 129.918,
      "endS": 132.761,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Fourteen sit unread right now, twenty eight are open,",
      "startS": 133.284,
      "endS": 135.351,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "and responses average around three hours.",
      "startS": 135.6,
      "endS": 139.479,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "Every row carries a status, a priority, and an owner,",
      "startS": 140.001,
      "endS": 143.554,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "so a billing question and a cancellation request never look alike.",
      "startS": 144.048,
      "endS": 147.771,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "Replying reaches a real customer.",
      "startS": 148.493,
      "endS": 150.362,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "We read the list and touch nothing.",
      "startS": 150.618,
      "endS": 152.72,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Portal Billing sits just under it.",
      "startS": 153.12,
      "endS": 155.224,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "A running log of billing events on the portal side.",
      "startS": 156.039,
      "endS": 158.615,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Card updates, plan changes, auto renewals,",
      "startS": 159.376,
      "endS": 164.959,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "and the failures that turn into phone calls.",
      "startS": 165.597,
      "endS": 168.047,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "When a member asks why a card was declined,",
      "startS": 168.405,
      "endS": 172.045,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "the action and status columns tell that story in one row.",
      "startS": 172.754,
      "endS": 174.778,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "Every line here is live money.",
      "startS": 175.242,
      "endS": 176.667,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "Read it, always; touch it, never.",
      "startS": 177.049,
      "endS": 178.4,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "Last entry, Portal Notifications.",
      "startS": 178.8,
      "endS": 181.4,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "The automated sends.",
      "startS": 181.688,
      "endS": 183.064,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "A welcome email fires when an account is created,",
      "startS": 183.675,
      "endS": 186.315,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "and a renewal reminder goes out a week ahead.",
      "startS": 186.66,
      "endS": 188.924,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "The list tracks each one's audience, open rate, and status.",
      "startS": 189.606,
      "endS": 192.876,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "Twelve are active, and more than eight hundred went out today alone.",
      "startS": 193.511,
      "endS": 196.926,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "These reach real members, so nothing here is ever sent, created, or edited in training.",
      "startS": 197.528,
      "endS": 203.197,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "So that's the Customer Portal group.",
      "startS": 203.6,
      "endS": 205.398,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p64",
      "text": "Five entries, and you have now read all five.",
      "startS": 205.895,
      "endS": 208.487,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p65",
      "text": "Portal Members for the roster and login trouble.",
      "startS": 209.62,
      "endS": 212.196,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p66",
      "text": "The booking page for what the customer actually sees.",
      "startS": 212.628,
      "endS": 215.368,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p67",
      "text": "Messages for the inbox, Billing for the money log, Notifications for the automated sends.",
      "startS": 215.884,
      "endS": 218.787,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p68",
      "text": "Reach them from the sidebar, since a pasted address still fails.",
      "startS": 219.081,
      "endS": 221.28,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p69",
      "text": "And read everything without sending, booking, or exporting a thing.",
      "startS": 221.822,
      "endS": 229.52,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}